snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
MatPat's Mario Party Birthday Surprise ►► http://bit.ly/1NISmQq
The Impossible Quiz: The Fail Begins! ►► http://bit.ly/1PqHnPO

It's a game we've all played plenty of times in our life - Would You Rather...? Steph and I debate the hard questions that the public wants to know about, such as "Would You Rather have fingers that were constantly coated in BBQ Sauce or Doritos' Cheese Powder?" Come find out way too much about us!

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.

HiLite: Ugliest MII Ever - Wii Sports ►► http://bit.ly/1WUF4Fa
HiLite: MatPat Chokes in Megaman ►► http://bit.ly/1S1lFBG
HiLite: Chubby Bunny Singoff  ►► http://bit.ly/1LzAN4D
snippet.title: Would You Rather? - StankPat BEGINS! (Part 1)
